  "pageTitle": "面向高价值塑料回收的光学分选设备",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-ai\"> <section class=\"section split-section\"> <div> <p class=\"eyebrow\">AI 光学分选</p> <h1>面向高价值塑料回收的光学分选设备</h1> <p class=\"hero-copy\">蔚澜 AI 光学分选设备通过材料和颜色识别 PET 瓶、HDPE 瓶、PP 及其他混合塑料。模块化配置支持自动废弃物分选系统、MRF 设备升级以及紧凑型智能回收设施，需要稳定的连续分拣。</p> <div class=\"hero-actions\"> <a class=\"text-link is-hud\" href=\"/contact\">请求提案</a></div></div> <picture> <source srcset=\"/assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.webp\" type=\"image/webp\"> <img src=\"/assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.png\" alt=\"AI 可回收塑料光学分选线\"></picture></section> <section class=\"section\" id=\"models\" aria-labelledby=\"models-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">型号数据</p> <h2 id=\"models-title\">型号范围由模块化光学分选配置定义</h2> <p>三种配置共用 AI 分选平台，可按吞吐量与物料类别选择。</p></div> <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-ai\"> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">迷你版</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\"> <dt>处理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\"> <dt>动力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\"> <dt>占地面积</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·8 × 3 m版面 ·3 m 净空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\"> <dt>分选范围</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明 PET·有色 PET·HDPE ·PP ·混合塑料\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">标准</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\"> <dt>处理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\"> <dt>动力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\"> <dt>占地面积</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·12 × 3 m版面 ·6 m 净空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\"> <dt>分选范围</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明 PET·绿色 PET ·蓝色 PET ·混色 PET·白色 HDPE·彩色 HDPE·PP ·混合塑料·剔除\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 颜色·HDPE ·PP ·混合·剔除</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Plus</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\"> <dt>处理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\"> <dt>动力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\"> <dt>占地面积</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安装占地 ·17 × 3 m版面 ·6 m 净空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <dt>分选范围</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>物料类型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分选范围：透明 PET·绿色 PET ·蓝色 PET ·混色 PET·白色 HDPE·彩色 HDPE·PP ·PE ·混合塑料·剔除\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 颜色·HDPE ·PP ·PE ·混合·剔除</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article></div></section> <section class=\"section sorting-performance-section\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-performance-title\"> <div class=\"sorting-performance-head\"> <div> <p class=\"eyebrow\">性能数据</p> <h2 id=\"sorting-performance-title\">分选性能由识别、控制与可改造模块共同驱动</h2> <p>GL01V 系列将 AI 识别、光学传感、气流喷射、循环输送和数字报告结合在一个紧凑的塑料回收和 MRF 升级分选中心中。</p></div></div> <div class=\"sorting-feed-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-feed-title\"> <div> <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">供料材料</p> <h3 id=\"sorting-feed-title\">物料识别范围</h3></div> <div class=\"sorting-feed-grid\" aria-label=\"常见塑料流示例\"> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-clear\"><b>PET</b><small>透明</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-green\"><b>PET</b><small>绿色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-blue\"><b>PET</b><small>蓝色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pet-mixed\"><b>PET</b><small>混色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe\"><b>HDPE</b><small>白色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe-colored\"><b>HDPE</b><small>有色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pp\"><b>PP</b><small>刚性</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pe\"><b>PE</b><small>目标</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-mixed\"><b>混合</b><small>塑料</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-reject\"><b>剔除</b><small>流</small></span></div></div> <div class=\"sorting-data-band\" aria-label=\"GL01V分选性能指标\"> <div class=\"sorting-data-copy\"> <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">紧凑分选中心</p> <h3>回收率与占地数据</h3> <p>Mini、Standard 和 Plus 布局从紧凑的试点产线扩展到更大规模的 MRF 试点产线，同时保持相同的 AI/HUD 操作逻辑。</p> <div class=\"sorting-mode-switch\" aria-label=\"布局状态\"> <span>工作</span> <span>运输</span></div></div> <div class=\"sorting-data-grid\"> <article> <span>类别</span> <strong>10<small>类上限</small></strong></article> <article> <span>处理能力</span> <strong>2<small>t/h 上限</small></strong></article> <article> <span>动力</span> <strong>30<small>千瓦下限</small></strong></article> <article> <span>占地面积</span> <strong>24<small>m<sup>2</sup> 下限</small></strong></article> <article> <span>布局</span> <strong>滑架<small>安装</small></strong></article> <article> <span>快速改装</span> <strong>17<small>天最快</small></strong></article></div></div> <div class=\"sorting-smart-panel\"> <div class=\"sorting-feature-intro\"> <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">智能机器</p> <h3>操作人员控制界面</h3></div> <div class=\"sorting-feature-grid\" aria-label=\"分选中心优势\"> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-ai\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>AI 识别</h3> <p>更高的回收价值：AI 可识别 PET、HDPE、PP、PE 与混合塑料，减少对人工判断的依赖。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-air\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>气喷分选</h3> <p>稳定输出纯度：快速的气流喷射能准确去除目标，同时处理线保持连续通量。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-sensors\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>传感器控制</h3> <p>降低纯度风险：实时传感器信号在输出质量下降前暴露识别、压力、时序和物料流漂移。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-rate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>96-98% 分选率</h3> <p>96-98%性能数据：宣传册中列出的高精度支持高纯度回收目标，用于塑料回收和 MRF 升级。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-robot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>可接入机器人的布局</h3> <p>降低劳动力压力：可接入机器人的布局为减少手工拣选留有空间，以适应物料体积增长。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-cockpit\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>数字驾驶舱</h3> <p>更快的决策：实时状态、警报、运行时间、分选统计、碳排放指示器和视频流都汇聚在同一视图中。</p></article></div></div></section> <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"plastic-process-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">工艺流程</p> <h2 id=\"plastic-process-title\">工艺控制从稳定给料延伸到数字化报告</h2> <p>光学分选系统围绕清晰的物料路径组织，项目团队可以据此评估给料、预分选、物料分选、颜色分选和运营数据在产线中的作用。</p></div> <ol class=\"process-timeline\" aria-label=\"塑料回收工艺\"> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-01</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>稳定给料</h3> <p>以受控速率将消费后的瓶子或混合的可回收塑料放入分选线。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"稳定给料过程视频\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\"> <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/AI上料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> 您的浏览器不支持视频播放。</video></div></figure></div></li> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-02</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>预分选接口</h3> <p>在下游分拣前，将金属集装箱与由其他材料制成的瓶子区分开来。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"预分选接口过程视频\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\"> <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/AI预分.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> 您的浏览器不支持视频播放。</video></div></figure></div></li> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-03</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>物料识别分选</h3> <p>按目标树脂类别区分塑料，以提高回收价值并减少人工依赖。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"材料分拣过程视频\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\"> <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/AI分拣.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> 您的浏览器不支持视频播放。</video></div></figure></div></li> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-04</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>颜色识别分选</h3> <p>按颜色 PET 瓶及其他目标材料分组，项目价值依赖于更清洁的比例。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"颜色识别分选过程视频\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\"> <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/AI出料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> 您的浏览器不支持视频播放。</video></div></figure></div></li> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-05</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>数字化报告输出</h3> <p>跟踪吞吐量、类别、设备状态、警报和碳排放相关操作指标。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"数字化报告输出视频占位符\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"视频即将发布\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-video-tag\">CAM-05</span> <span class=\"process-timeline-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <span class=\"process-timeline-video-label\">视频即将发布</span></div></figure></div></li></ol></section> <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" aria-labelledby=\"compare-title\" hidden> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">对比数据</p> <h2 id=\"compare-title\">对比数据覆盖占地、产能、功耗与装配效率</h2> <p>以下对比围绕占地、产能、功耗和装配效率，帮助评估光学分选线的总拥有成本。</p></div> <div class=\"product-compare-layout\"> <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"GL01V爆炸视角\"> <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"爆炸视图图即将发布\"> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-tag\">爆炸 ·GL01V2-9</span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:18%;--pin-y:32%\" data-label=\"01\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:38%;--pin-y:58%\" data-label=\"02\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:58%;--pin-y:26%\" data-label=\"03\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:74%;--pin-y:64%\" data-label=\"04\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:88%;--pin-y:40%\" data-label=\"05\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-label\">爆炸视角即将上线</span></div> <figcaption> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">5 模块化滑橇·标准模具</span></figcaption></figure> <div class=\"product-compare-panel\"> <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>蔚澜 GL01V</span> <span class=\"product-compare-legend\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>行业基线</span></header> <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\"> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span> <h3>局部与整机比例</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">单位成本占比</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:38%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">38%</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">62%</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">较低的备件比例意味着折旧更慢，寿命周期维护成本更低。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span> <h3>占地面积</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">标准层为m²</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:55%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">36 m²</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">65 m²</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">滑架式布局适合紧凑的 MRF 房间和路边回收站。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span> <h3>处理能力</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">t/h，标准等级</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:88%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.8 – 1.2</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.6 – 0.9</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">优化给料 + AI 识别提升了相同占地等级的吞吐量。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span> <h3>功耗</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">千瓦，标准级别</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:60%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">45 kW</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">75 kW</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">按额定吞吐量计算，每吨分拣功率约降低40%。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-05</span> <h3>运输与组装</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">现场安装天数</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:35%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">3 – 5 天</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:90%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基线</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">10 – 14 天</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">预接线滑架模块以标准集装箱出厂；现场工作主要为螺栓固定和线缆连接。</p></li></ul></div></div></section> <section class=\"section ai-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-faq-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">常见问题</p> <h2 id=\"ai-faq-title\">配置判断从物料数据、产出目标与现场接口开始</h2> <p>这些答案帮助回收操作人员、EPC 团队和设备采购者评估蔚澜 AI 光学分选机是否适合其物料流和项目阶段。</p></div> <div class=\"ai-faq-panel\"> <article class=\"ai-faq-item\"> <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-01</span>物料分离范围</h3> <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">该系统设计用于可回收塑料流，如 PET 瓶、HDPE 瓶、PP、混合硬塑料以及颜色基 PET 分组，包括透明瓶、绿色瓶、蓝色瓶和混合色瓶。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span> <span>物料照片或视频</span> <span>目标产出类别</span></div></article> <article class=\"ai-faq-item\"> <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-02</span>价格因素依据</h3> <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">价格取决于吞吐量、物料类别、分选模块数量、送料和打包范围、数字控制需求、安装支持，以及项目是否需要与现有 MRF 设备集成。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span> <span>目标吞吐量</span> <span>分选模块范围</span></div></article> <article class=\"ai-faq-item\"> <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-03</span>光学分选产能范围</h3> <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">GL01V 系列覆盖 0.6-2 t/h。最终选型应结合物料组成、污染程度、目标纯度、可用占地面积及每日运行时间进行评估。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span> <span>每日运营时间</span> <span>可用占地面积</span></div></article> <article class=\"ai-faq-item\"> <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-04</span>现有设施集成</h3> <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">当项目方提供当前工艺布局、进料状况、输送机高度、控制需求和目标输出时，可以评估整合性。滑架安装结构支持实用改装讨论。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需输入</span> <span>现有产线布局</span> <span>输送机高度与控制点</span></div></article></div></section> <section class=\"section ai-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-rfq-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ 输入资料</p> <h2 id=\"ai-rfq-title\">尺寸选型精度取决于物料资料、吞吐量、产出与布局输入</h2> <p>在报价前发送这些输入，以便工程团队确认分选范围、设备型号、布局可行性和集成风险。</p></div> <div class=\"ai-rfq-checklist\"> <article> <span>01</span> <h3>物料照片或视频</h3> <p>显示输送带上的进料流、打包状态、污染程度，以及正常运行条件下的颜色混合情况。</p></article> <article> <span>02</span> <h3>目标吞吐量</h3> <p>确认每小时处理能力、每日的运营时间、高峰负荷，以及处理线是否需要一个或多个分选模块。</p></article> <article> <span>03</span> <h3>产出类别</h3> <p>列出所需的产出组分，例如透明 PET、绿色 PET、蓝色 PET、HDPE、PP、混合塑料或剔除流。</p></article> <article> <span>04</span> <h3>现有产线布局</h3> <p>提供输送机高度、可用占地面积、上游送料方式、下游打包机位置及控制接口需求。</p></article></div> <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\"> <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求工程评审</a> <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">准备文件包</a></div></section></main>"
}
